<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en-GB">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>The Matts - Finding Responsible AI-Enabled Working</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --apple-blue: #0071e3;
            --apple-text-primary: #1d1d1f;
            --apple-text-secondary: #86868b;
            --apple-bg-page: #f5f5f7;
            --apple-bg-card: #ffffff;
            --radius-card: 22px;
            --radius-button: 980px;
            --shadow-card: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
            --shadow-hover: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            --font-stack: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "SF Pro Text", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            --transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.1, 0.25, 1);
        }

        body {
            font-family: var(--font-stack);
            background-color: var(--apple-bg-page);
            color: var(--apple-text-primary);
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
            -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
            line-height: 1.47059;
            letter-spacing: -0.022em;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 980px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 40px 22px;
        }

        /* Navigation */
        .global-nav {
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 9999;
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            backdrop-filter: saturate(180%) blur(20px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: saturate(180%) blur(20px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            height: 48px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .nav-content { display: flex; gap: 30px; }

        .global-nav a {
            color: var(--apple-text-primary);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 400;
            opacity: 0.8;
            transition: opacity 0.2s ease;
        }

        .global-nav a:hover { opacity: 1; color: var(--apple-blue); }

        /* Header */
        header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 80px 0 50px;
            animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease-out;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 56px;
            line-height: 1.07143;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: -0.005em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .subtitle {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 400;
            letter-spacing: 0.009em;
            color: var(--apple-text-secondary);
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }

        .tagline {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: var(--apple-blue);
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 0.02em;
            margin-top: 6px;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 40px;
            line-height: 1.1;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        h3 { font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600; }

        /* Cards */
        .section-card {
            background: var(--apple-bg-card);
            border-radius: var(--radius-card);
            padding: 60px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-card);
        }

        /* Accordions */
        details { border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e5ea; }
        details:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

        summary {
            padding: 24px 0;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 19px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--apple-text-primary);
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            outline: none;
        }

        summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }

        summary::after {
            content: '+';
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 300;
            color: var(--apple-blue);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            margin-left: 16px;
        }

        details[open] summary::after { transform: rotate(45deg); }
        details[open] summary { color: var(--apple-blue); }

        .details-content {
            padding-bottom: 30px;
            animation: slideDown 0.3s ease-out;
        }

        @keyframes slideDown {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-10px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        /* Consistent exercise note across all exercises */
        .exercise-note {
            font-size: 15px;
            color: var(--apple-text-secondary);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: 500;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        /* Prompt box */
        .prompt-box {
            background-color: #f5f5f7;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-family: "SF Mono", Menlo, monospace;
            font-size: 13px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            margin: 10px 0 15px 0;
            white-space: pre-wrap;
            border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }

        /* Buttons */
        .btn-copy {
            background-color: #e8e8ed;
            color: var(--apple-text-primary);
            font-size: 12px;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: var(--radius-button);
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: background-color 0.2s;
        }

        .btn-copy:hover { background-color: #d2d2d7; }

        /* Exercise badge */
        .exercise-label {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
        }

        .ex-badge {
            background: var(--apple-blue);
            color: white;
            font-size: 10px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 0.06em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            padding: 4px 10px;
            border-radius: 980px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        /* Contact */
        .contact-link { color: var(--apple-blue); text-decoration: none; }
        .contact-link:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 0;
            color: var(--apple-text-secondary);
            font-size: 12px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e5ea;
            margin-top: 60px;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        @media (max-width: 734px) {
            h1 { font-size: 40px; }
            h2 { font-size: 32px; }
            .section-card { padding: 30px 24px; }
            .container { padding-top: 20px; }
        }
    </style>
    <script>
        function copyToClipboard(id) {
            const promptText = document.getElementById(id).innerText;
            navigator.clipboard.writeText(promptText).then(() => {
                const button = document.querySelector(`button[onclick="copyToClipboard('${id}')"]`);
                const originalText = button.innerText;
                button.innerText = "Copied";
                button.style.backgroundColor = "#34c759";
                button.style.color = "white";
                setTimeout(() => {
                    button.innerText = originalText;
                    button.style.backgroundColor = "#e8e8ed";
                    button.style.color = "var(--apple-text-primary)";
                }, 2000);
            });
        }
    </script>
</head>
<body>

    <nav class="global-nav">
        <div class="nav-content">
            <a href="#exercises">Exercises</a>
            <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="container">

        <header>
            <h1>The Matts Workshop</h1>
            <div class="subtitle">Finding Responsible AI-Enabled Working</div>
            <div class="tagline">AI in the Workplace</div>
        </header>

        <!-- Exercises -->
        <section id="exercises" class="section-card">
            <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 50px;">
                <h2>Workshop Exercises</h2>
                <p style="color: var(--apple-text-secondary); max-width: 560px; margin: 10px auto 0 auto; font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.5;">
                    Work through each exercise in order. Copy and paste prompts directly into <a href="https://m365copilot.com/" target="_blank" style="color:var(--apple-blue); text-decoration:none; font-weight:600;">Microsoft Copilot</a> and click <strong style="color: var(--apple-text-primary);">"New Chat"</strong> between each exercise.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Exercise 1 -->
            <details open>
                <summary>
                    <span class="exercise-label">
                        <span class="ex-badge">Exercise 1</span>
                        AI Discovery Sprint
                    </span>
                </summary>
                <div class="details-content">
                    <div class="exercise-note">
                        <strong>Application:</strong> Find your next AI Experiment! Just think could this be useful? 5mins to look at upto a 100 AI usage cases.
                    </div>

                    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr)); gap: 16px;">
                        <a href="sprint.html" target="_blank" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; background: #f0f7ff; border: 1px solid rgba(0,113,227,0.2); border-radius: 16px; padding: 24px; text-decoration: none; color: var(--apple-text-primary); transition: var(--transition);" onmouseover="this.style.boxShadow='0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.08)'" onmouseout="this.style.boxShadow='none'">
                            <div style="font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 10px;">&#9889;</div>
                            <span style="font-size: 17px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 6px; color: var(--apple-blue);">Open Discovery Sprint</span>
                            <span style="font-size: 14px; color: var(--apple-text-secondary); line-height: 1.5; flex-grow: 1;">Interactive activity with a 5-minute timer. Find your AI use cases.</span>
                        </a>

                        <a href="usagecases.html" target="_blank" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; background: #f5f5f7; border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.04); border-radius: 16px; padding: 24px; text-decoration: none; color: var(--apple-text-primary); transition: var(--transition);" onmouseover="this.style.boxShadow='0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.08)'" onmouseout="this.style.boxShadow='none'">
                            <div style="font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 10px;">&#128218;</div>
                            <span style="font-size: 17px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 6px;">Backup: 100 AI Use Cases</span>
                            <span style="font-size: 14px; color: var(--apple-text-secondary); line-height: 1.5; flex-grow: 1;">Browse the full library of prompts if the sprint is not loading.</span>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </details>

            <!-- Exercise 2 -->
            <details open>
                <summary>
                    <span class="exercise-label">
                        <span class="ex-badge">Exercise 2</span>
                        Explain It Like I'm 5 (ELI5)
                    </span>
                </summary>
                <div class="details-content">
                    <div class="exercise-note">
                        <strong>Application:</strong> Quickly understand complex topics or prepare simple, jargon-free explanations for humans.
                    </div>

                    <div class="prompt-box" id="eli5-prompt">"Explain [TOPIC] to me like I am 5 (ELI5)"</div>
                    <button onclick="copyToClipboard('eli5-prompt')" class="btn-copy">Copy Prompt</button>

                    <p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 13px; color: var(--apple-text-secondary);">
                        <em>Replace [TOPIC] with something relevant to your work. Try: "AI-Enabled working with Copilot Chat", "machine learning", "procurement frameworks", or "the offside rule in football".</em>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </details>

            <!-- Exercise 3 -->
            <details open>
                <summary>
                    <span class="exercise-label">
                        <span class="ex-badge">Exercise 3</span>
                        Let AI Write Prompts for You
                    </span>
                </summary>
                <div class="details-content">
                    <div class="exercise-note">
                        <strong>Application:</strong> Paste this  prompt into Copilot, then describe any repetitive task. Copilot will generate 3 ready-to-use prompts tailored to your work.
                    </div>

                    <div class="prompt-box" id="meta-prompt-helper">"You help people use AI prompts in Microsoft Copilot Chat to speed up repetitive work tasks.

When a user describes a task:
* Ask 1-2 clarifying questions if needed
* Suggest 3 ready-to-use prompts they can copy into Copilot Chat

Only suggest prompts that work with text the user pastes in themselves. No email, calendar, or app access. Skip any part of the task where AI genuinely wouldn't help.

Start by asking: 'What repetitive task would you like help with?'"</div>
                    <button onclick="copyToClipboard('meta-prompt-helper')" class="btn-copy">Copy Prompt</button>

                    <p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 13px; color: var(--apple-text-secondary);">
                        <em>Try: "I spend a lot of time writing meeting summaries" or "I categorise customer feedback emails every Monday".</em>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </details>

            <!-- Exercise 4 -->
            <details open>
                <summary>
                    <span class="exercise-label">
                        <span class="ex-badge">Exercise 4</span>
                        Create My First Agent
                    </span>
                </summary>
                <div class="details-content">
                    <div class="exercise-note">
                        <strong>Application:</strong> Agents are reusable Copilot assistants with a specific focus. Build one once, use it every day, and share it with your team.
                    </div>

                    <ol style="padding-left: 20px; line-height: 1.8; font-size: 15px; margin: 0;">
                        <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
                            <strong>Open Copilot</strong> - Go to <a href="https://m365copilot.com" target="_blank" style="color: var(--apple-blue); text-decoration: none;">m365copilot.com</a> and click <strong>"Create agent"</strong> in the left-hand menu.
                        </li>
                        <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
                            <strong>Enter the Description</strong> - In the "Describe" tab, type the following and hit the submit arrow:
                            <br><br>
                            <em style="font-size: 14px;">"The user will provide a word and you must generate 3 possible crossword style clues for that word"</em>
                        </li>
                        <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
                            <strong>Click Create</strong> - You may be prompted to name your agent. Reply to that, then click <strong>Create</strong>.
                        </li>
                        <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
                            <strong>Click Go to Agent</strong> - Wait for the success message, then click the blue <strong>"Go to Agent"</strong> button.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Test It</strong> - Type a single word like <strong>"Book"</strong> and check it generates 3 crossword clues.
                        </li>
                    </ol>
                </div>
            </details>

            <!-- Exercise 5 -->
            <details open>
                <summary>
                    <span class="exercise-label">
                        <span class="ex-badge">Exercise 5</span>
                        Process Mapping Your Work
                    </span>
                </summary>
                <div class="details-content">
                    <div class="exercise-note">
                        <strong>Application:</strong> Before you can improve a process, you need to understand it. Use Post-it notes to map a real task from your role, find the pain points, and spot where AI or automation could help.
                    </div>

                    <!-- Colour legend -->
                    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 14px; margin-bottom: 28px;">
                        <div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 14px; background: #f5f5f7; border-radius: 14px; padding: 18px;">
                            <div style="background: #f7e84e; border-radius: 8px; width: 44px; height: 44px; flex-shrink: 0; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 800; color: #5c4b00; letter-spacing: 0.03em; text-align: center; line-height: 1.2;">YEL&shy;LOW</div>
                            <div>
                                <p style="font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 3px 0;">Steps</p>
                                <p style="font-size: 13px; color: var(--apple-text-secondary); margin: 0 0 5px 0; line-height: 1.4;">Each step in the process. One action per note.</p>
                                <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #8a7a30; margin: 0; font-style: italic;">"Send email" / "Check form"</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 14px; background: #f5f5f7; border-radius: 14px; padding: 18px;">
                            <div style="background: #f0899a; border-radius: 8px; width: 44px; height: 44px; flex-shrink: 0; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 800; color: #6b0018; letter-spacing: 0.03em;">PINK</div>
                            <div>
                                <p style="font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 3px 0;">Problems</p>
                                <p style="font-size: 13px; color: var(--apple-text-secondary); margin: 0 0 5px 0; line-height: 1.4;">Delays, errors, or anything that wastes time.</p>
                                <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #8a3040; margin: 0; font-style: italic;">"Wait 3 days for approval"</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 14px; background: #f5f5f7; border-radius: 14px; padding: 18px;">
                            <div style="background: #f5b942; border-radius: 8px; width: 44px; height: 44px; flex-shrink: 0; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 800; color: #6b3a00; letter-spacing: 0.03em; text-align: center; line-height: 1.2;">ORAN&shy;GE</div>
                            <div>
                                <p style="font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 3px 0;">Automate</p>
                                <p style="font-size: 13px; color: var(--apple-text-secondary); margin: 0 0 5px 0; line-height: 1.4;">Steps where AI or Power Automate could take over.</p>
                                <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #8a5000; margin: 0; font-style: italic;">Write "PA", "AI", or "PA+AI"</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Step 1 -->
                    <div style="display: flex; gap: 18px; align-items: flex-start; background: #f5f5f7; border-radius: 14px; padding: 20px 22px; margin-bottom: 14px;">
                        <div style="background: var(--apple-blue); color: white; border-radius: 50%; width: 36px; height: 36px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px;">1</div>
                        <div>
                            <p style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 6px 0;">Map the Steps</p>
                            <p style="font-size: 14px; color: var(--apple-text-secondary); margin: 0; line-height: 1.6;">Identify the start and end of your process. Write every action on a yellow note. Stick them on the wall left to right. Map what <strong>actually happens</strong>, not what you wish happened.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Step 2 -->
                    <div style="display: flex; gap: 18px; align-items: flex-start; background: #fff0f3; border: 1px solid #f5c6ce; border-radius: 14px; padding: 20px 22px; margin-bottom: 14px;">
                        <div style="background: #f0899a; color: white; border-radius: 50%; width: 36px; height: 36px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px;">2</div>
                        <div style="width: 100%;">
                            <p style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 6px 0;">Find the Problems</p>
                            <p style="font-size: 14px; color: var(--apple-text-secondary); margin: 0 0 14px 0; line-height: 1.6;">Walk the map. Stick a pink note next to any step that causes delays, errors, or frustration. Ask yourself:</p>
                            <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 12px;">
                                <div style="background: white; border-left: 3px solid #f0899a; border-radius: 6px; padding: 12px 14px;">
                                    <p style="font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 4px 0;">Where do you wait?</p>
                                    <p style="font-size: 13px; color: var(--apple-text-secondary); margin: 0; line-height: 1.4;">For approvals, replies, access, or someone else to finish</p>
                                </div>
                                <div style="background: white; border-left: 3px solid #f0899a; border-radius: 6px; padding: 12px 14px;">
                                    <p style="font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 4px 0;">Where do mistakes happen?</p>
                                    <p style="font-size: 13px; color: var(--apple-text-secondary); margin: 0; line-height: 1.4;">Wrong data, missing info, duplicated effort, wrong versions</p>
                                </div>
                                <div style="background: white; border-left: 3px solid #f0899a; border-radius: 6px; padding: 12px 14px;">
                                    <p style="font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 4px 0;">What is boring or repetitive?</p>
                                    <p style="font-size: 13px; color: var(--apple-text-secondary); margin: 0; line-height: 1.4;">Copy-paste, re-typing, chasing people, manual checking</p>
                                </div>
                                <div style="background: white; border-left: 3px solid #f0899a; border-radius: 6px; padding: 12px 14px;">
                                    <p style="font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 4px 0;">What takes way too long?</p>
                                    <p style="font-size: 13px; color: var(--apple-text-secondary); margin: 0; line-height: 1.4;">Steps that eat up time compared to the value they add</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div style="background: #e8f4fd; border-radius: 8px; padding: 11px 14px; font-size: 14px; color: #0056b3; line-height: 1.5;">
                                Clusters of pink = process hotspots. These are where you will get the biggest wins from fixing or automating.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Step 3 -->
                    <div style="display: flex; gap: 18px; align-items: flex-start; background: #fff8ee; border: 1px solid #f5d9a8; border-radius: 14px; padding: 20px 22px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                        <div style="background: #f5b942; color: white; border-radius: 50%; width: 36px; height: 36px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px;">3</div>
                        <div style="width: 100%;">
                            <p style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 6px 0;">Spot the AI/Automation</p>
                            <p style="font-size: 14px; color: var(--apple-text-secondary); margin: 0 0 14px 0; line-height: 1.6;">Look at your steps, especially the pink ones. Add an orange note where you think technology could help. Write PA, AI, or both.</p>
                            <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 12px;">
                                <div style="background: white; border-top: 3px solid var(--apple-blue); border-radius: 6px; padding: 12px 14px;">
                                    <p style="font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 5px 0;">Write "PA" - Power Automate</p>
                                    <p style="font-size: 13px; color: var(--apple-text-secondary); margin: 0; line-height: 1.4;">Tasks that follow clear rules and are the same every time. Moving data, sending reminders, filing documents.</p>
                                </div>
                                <div style="background: white; border-top: 3px solid #00897b; border-radius: 6px; padding: 12px 14px;">
                                    <p style="font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 5px 0;">Write "AI" - Copilot</p>
                                    <p style="font-size: 13px; color: var(--apple-text-secondary); margin: 0; line-height: 1.4;">Tasks that need reading, writing, or making sense of information. Drafting, summarising, answering questions.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div style="background: #e8f4fd; border-radius: 8px; padding: 11px 14px; font-size: 14px; color: #0056b3; line-height: 1.5;">
                                Some steps need both. Power Automate to trigger it, AI to do the thinking. Write "PA+AI" on those.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <p style="font-size: 14px; color: var(--apple-text-secondary); line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;">
                        <strong style="color: var(--apple-text-primary);">Hold onto your map.</strong> You will use it in Exercise 6.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </details>

            <!-- Exercise 6 -->
            <details open>
                <summary>
                    <span class="exercise-label">
                        <span class="ex-badge">Exercise 6</span>
                        Copilot Reads Your Process Map
                    </span>
                </summary>
                <div class="details-content">
                    <div class="exercise-note">
                        <strong>Application:</strong> Copilot can analyse images. Take a photo of your Post-it map, upload it, and let Copilot suggest where AI could help across your process.
                    </div>

                    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 14px; margin-bottom: 24px;">
